CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 7, 1949, pg. 17 reads: "The Chapelettes - Completing plans for "Romance in Spring," a garden scene pageant, which will be featured at Brown Chapel AME, Friday, June 13, at 8:15 o'clock. Seated: Mmes. Sarah Chadwick, president, and Viola Horton, secretary.  Standing: Mmes. L. Young, O. Dandridge, sponsor, and Luella Leonard, treasurer.  The Rev. J.L. Dandridge is pastor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Chapelettes club members, from left, seated: Sarah Chadwick and Viola Horton; standing: Mrs. L. Young, Mrs. O. Dandridge, and Luella Leonard, gathered around dining room table in domestic interior
